overview: Work From Home Wizards was founded in 2006 and caters to writers and publishers who need constant access to new work at home venues. They carry 1000’s of new writing job listings at all times and are always updating their database with the freshest of writing jobs. Work From Home Wizards works as a middleman for writers and contractors for story, article, and blog writing, and because they have such a large list of contractors, there are endless writing jobs for you to choose from. If you are looking for a way to make real money and work from home, then Work From Home Wizards is a great place to do that.
